run NodeSweep-61-20260517-18:31:05-1261
attr configname NodeSweep
attr datetime 20260517-18:31:05
attr datetimef 20260517-183105
attr experiment NodeSweep
attr inifile omnetpp.ini
attr iterationvars $N=50
attr iterationvarsd N=50
attr iterationvarsf N=50-
attr measurement $N=50
attr network SmartLoRaNetwork
attr processid 1261
attr repetition 1
